Description: SLM Desktop system installer
 Calamares-based installer that provisions an SLM Desktop system with a
 UEFI-only, Btrfs-rooted layout and a self-contained recovery partition.
 Onboarding (theme, account, AI, nearby) is handled by slm-welcome on first
 login, not by this installer.
